but I thought you would
love it.

14:03.961 --> 14:07.086
- Frances, no way.
- Yes way.

14:13.462 --> 14:14.753
It's gorgeous.

14:16.044 --> 14:18.712
I'm an asshole.
I have nothing for you.

14:18.712 --> 14:21.211
Are you kidding me?
Look around.

14:21.211 --> 14:26.295
You-- you have
