you will ever know.

14:31.003 --> 14:31.961
Thank you.

14:31.961 --> 14:33.253
Okay, go.
Go, go, go.

14:33.253 --> 14:34.753
- Don't do that. Go.

14:36.253 --> 14:38.712
Oh, God, I'm so nervous.
I'm so nervous,

14:38.712 --> 14:41.628
