14:44.336 --> 14:45.503
- Yeah.

14:45.503 --> 14:47.044
Oh, my God.

14:47.044 --> 14:48.253
Oh, my God!

14:48.253 --> 14:49.670
This time you gotta
introduce me.

14:49.670 --> 14:50.836
Okay.

14:52.670 --> 14:53.919
Hello, welcome!

14:53.919 --> 14:55.211
Welcome.
- Hi.

14:55.211 --> 14:57.086
I don't know
if your presence--

14:57.086 --> 15:00.378
does that mean it was, like,
the shortest board meeting
in Whitney history?

15:00.378 --> 15:03.336
