16:19.712 --> 16:21.378
- Yeah, yeah.
- Okay, good talk.

16:21.378 --> 16:23.378
Frances:
Okay, bar's over here.

16:26.587 --> 16:28.545
- Sold!
- Love it.

16:28.545 --> 16:30.211
