feel impolite accepting

17:11.587 --> 17:13.712
when I'm-- I'm here
with someone else.

17:13.712 --> 17:16.253
Oh.
That Andrew fellow?

17:16.253 --> 17:19.919
Wow. Too bad.
Good luck.

17:24.878 --> 17:27.462
Ay. Oh, hey.

17:27.462 --> 17:29.503
Uh, I've been
floating around all night.

17:29.503 --> 17:31.503
- I don't want you
to feel neglected.
