17:41.086 --> 17:43.170
- Mm-hmm.

17:43.170 --> 17:45.003
- Diane: Ugh.

17:45.003 --> 17:46.336
Get a room.

17:46.336 --> 17:47.961
Why did I even bother
showing up tonight?

17:47.961 --> 17:51.211
- I'm a vapor.
