17:55.420 --> 17:57.545
- Woman: Shh, shh, shh.
- Diane: Nick!

18:01.170 --> 18:03.295
Hi, everyone.

18:03.295 --> 18:06.253
Nick Clavowen,
friend of the gallery.

18:06.253 --> 18:08.878
I-- I know
Frances and Sylvia

18:08.878 --> 18:11.044
