to tonight's proceedings--

18:20.003 --> 18:22.378
my wife,
Diane Clavowen.

18:22.378 --> 18:24.378
- Crowd: Aw!

18:27.587 --> 18:30.919
- Without Diane...

18:30.919 --> 18:33.628
this masterpiece...

18:35.253 --> 18:38.919
...by Eliot Pelts
would never have been
loaned to the gallery.

18:38.919 --> 18:40.878
Man, it looks like
a toilet monster.

18:40.878 --> 18:45.961
Sadly, after tonight,
the Pelts will be leaving
for another home.

18:45.961 --> 18:48.336
- Ours.

18:48.336 --> 18:51.420
- Purchased
from Brett Morris.

18:51.420 --> 18:53.628
Just a little surprise
from me to you.

18:53.628 --> 18:56.336
- One more way to say,
"I love you, Diane."

18:56.336 --> 18:57.919
- All: Aw.

18:57.919 --> 18:59.128
Nick.

19:02.587 --> 19:06.253
- Halle-fucking-lujah.
- Yeah, this is a win-win.

19:06.253 --> 19:08.919
You should be crying
and thanking him, too.

19:13.295 --> 19:16.044
Ted?
Oh, my God, hi.

19:16.044 --> 19:19.003
