in the city.

26:29.044 --> 26:31.378
I know, it's crazy.

26:31.378 --> 26:33.128
I'm freaking out.

26:34.878 --> 26:35.878
What?
Say something.

26:38.211 --> 26:42.128
And, um--
and you have--

26:42.128 --> 26:44.295
have you--
you've accepted his offer?

26:44.295 --> 26:46.295
Well, yeah, sure.

26:46.295 --> 26:49.503
You understand this means

26:49.503 --> 26:52.044
that we won't be
working together anymore.

26:54.086 --> 26:56.211
- You and I.
- I know, it sucks, but--

26:56.211 --> 26:58.836
- This is a really big deal.

26:58.836 --> 27:00.462
I thought you'd be
happy for me.

27:00.462 --> 27:03.378
No, I am, I am.
I'm just also stunned,
you know?

27:03.378 --> 27:06.336
Because I-- I mean,
I know we didn't have--

27:06.336 --> 27:08.961
um, we didn't have
a formal agreement,

27:08.961 --> 27:13.878
but, um, I did think that
we had an understanding.

27:13.878 --> 27:17.628
You know, I mean,
we've been talking
about your next show.

27:17.628 --> 27:22.587
We have-- we  have been
talking about your future.

27:24.253 --> 27:29.794
And now...
and now you--

27:29.794 --> 27:31.211
I what?

27:31.211 --> 27:34.128
You didn't even
have the decency

27:34.128 --> 27:37.295
to tell me
that you were having
this conversation with Skip

27:37.295 --> 27:42.295
so that I could
at least, like, try
to compete for you.

27:42.295 --> 27:45.462
You weren't even
finishing your paintings
when I met you.

27:45.462 --> 27:47.919
Yeah, but then
I finished them.

27:47.919 --> 27:52.587
Yes, and I scraped
this show together

27:52.587 --> 27:54.919
with spit and blood.

27:54.919 --> 27:56.919
We sold every single piece.

27:56.919 --> 28:00.836
- That's, like, just--
that's unheard of.
- Yeah, you're right.

28:00.836 --> 28:03.420
If it weren't for you,
I'd still be at the bank.

28:03.420 --> 28:04.961
But get real.

28:04.961 --> 28:07.794
If you were in my shoes,
you'd do the same thing.

28:07.794 --> 28:09.378
Really, get real?

28:09.378 --> 28:10.919
You get real.

28:10.919 --> 28:12.420
You waited the whole meal

28:12.420 --> 28:14.378
to give me
this bit of information

28:14.378 --> 28:17.628
because you knew
it was going to be awful.

28:17.628 --> 28:19.628
Okay, but it doesn't
have to be.

28:19.628 --> 28:21.211
It's not personal,
Frances.

28:21.211 --> 28:22.628
It's not personal?

28:22.628 --> 28:26.295
Okay, you know what?
I don't need the guilt trip.

28:26.295 --> 28:28.919
Thanks for everything.
I'm done here.

